01:20:26.899 --> 01:20:30.597
Huh? I'm sorry, ma'am.
Have a nice day then.

01:20:33.566 --> 01:20:35.500
My wife's in Italy.

01:20:36.899 --> 01:20:39.368
What the helI's
she doing in Italy?

01:20:39.433 --> 01:20:41.264
